HEADWORD: Tactical
<hw>Tac"tic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>taktiko`s</grk>. See
<er>tactics</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to military or naval
tactics; hence, pertaining to, or characterized by, planning or
maneuvering for the short term; -- contrasted with
<contr>strategic</contr>, planning for the long term.</def>⟦br⟧
-- <wordforms><wf>Tac"tic*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
